                            <div class="row clearfix">
                                <div class="col-md-5 col-md-offset-1 col-xs-offset-1 col-xs-10">
                                    <div class="welcome-bg">
                                        <div class="green-heading">Welcome to Italy...abroad</div>
                                        <div class="welcome-text">
                                            <p>At Italyabroad.com we only work with small and passionate wine makers and artisans, we only sell the wine and food we love</p>
                                            <p>We don’t tell fairytales to justify huge discounts and ridiculous prices, the only stories we tell are the ones of our producers and ours and why we love them</p>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="welcome-btn"><a href="<%=session[:return_path]%>"><img src="landing-img/get-excited-btn.png" alt="get excited" /></a></div>
